Immediate Issues Found
1. ATS scan never fires on re-visit — dataRef is useRef, resets on unmount. Need module-level.
2. Import has zero data validation — raw JSON passes straight to state. Missing fields cause silent failures.
3. INITIAL_RESUME_DATA is incomplete — missing 6 optional sections vs EMPTY_RESUME_TEMPLATE.
4. No text/PDF import — only JSON.
5. Import buried in Settings — user has to click Settings → Data Management → Import. No dedicated import entry point.
6. PDF/Word import button exists in ResumePreview but onTriggerImport prop is never wired to anything.
